and rearers.</p><p>\"The animal welfare strategy ... will ultimately deliver world-class levels of care for all racing greyhounds,\" she said.</p><p>In its submission to a NSW parliamentary inquiry into the greyhound racing industry on Thursday, the RSPCA said overbreeding had led to thousands of dogs being euthanased when they failed as racers.</p><p>\"There's clear evidence of mass overbreeding of greyhounds in NSW resulting in a vast population of surplus unwanted dogs,\" said RSPCA Australia scientific officer Jade Norris.</p>","headline":"Greyhound racing imposes tighter rules on owners and breeders","trailText":"New animal welfare regulations follow criticism that thousands of dogs are put down each year due to overbreeding","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"theguardian.com","showInRelatedContent":"true","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3mg25","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/6/1391666046133/5d7e3000-9042-445d-8824-cd3d3aa68dee-140x84.jpeg","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/6/1391666046133/5d7e3000-9042-445d-8824-cd3d3aa68dee-140x84.jpeg","wordcount":"172","commentable":"false","internalContentCode":"429031326","allowUgc":"false","internalComposerCode":"52f320aae4b0ab978b0f974f","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Australian Associated Press","newspaperEditionDate":"2014-02-06T00:00:00Z","internalPageCode":"2039072","productionOffice":"AUS","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-02-09T05:55:43Z"},"rights":{"syndicatable":false,"subscriptionDatabases":false},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/feb/06/greyhound-racing-imposes-tighter-rules","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/world/2014/feb/06/greyhound-racing-imposes-tighter-rules","tags":[{"id":"world/animal-welfare","webTitle":"Animal welfare","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/animal-welfare","a